                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Resumen de Compra</h5>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-2">
                        <span>Subtotal:</span>
